{"tid":1492083,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[聯署] 要求美國撤銷涉事中國留學生嘅student visa","createTime":"2019-08-20T16:20:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T18:57:38.000Z","uid":276215,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"32c03d3917590702d53c59a9338a6cbc0a325638","tid":1492083,"uid":276215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:20:12.000Z","msg":"利申P牌仔，同意唔該幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">不如一齊聯署要求Trump administration進一步限制中國人入讀美國嘅大學，收緊收生要求，甚至即時revoke涉事中國留學生嘅student visa</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>1) 全世界遍地開花嘅和平集會，多次有中國留學生拉大隊高舉中國國旗搗亂 / 毆打集會人士</strong><br />\n佢地嘅不文明行為嚴重損害世界各國市民嘅集會自由、危害和平示威者嘅人身安全，甚至可能殃及聲援香港嘅本地人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>2) 阻止共產黨利用中國研究生竊取美國嘅知識產權，同埋利用中國留學生滲透美國、危害國家安全</strong><br />\n其實呢方面美國已經做緊野，例如特定學系嘅研究生只准批一年visa、經常拒批工作簽證等等。我地只需要打香港牌，要求侵侵再加碼趕絕強國人，保障香港留學生嘅人身安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.latimes.com/california/story/2019-07-21/uc-china-trump-trade-visa\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.latimes.com%2Fcalifornia%2Fstory%2F2019-07-21%2Fuc-china-trump-trade-visa&d=DXuv2gayA%2Byyjyt3RGK41JS3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=e5316885\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.latimes.com/california/story/2019-07-21/uc-china-trump-trade-visa</a>"},{"pid":"e2309b9b12aaa1f1941a18e8bd35fe408e2993e8","tid":1492083,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:20:25.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"52d85ae4bd287437600c75d7584c5d8d0bbc9897","tid":1492083,"uid":66221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:20:50.000Z","msg":"趕走小粉紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4a39c7592e682abef62c8c1a621d67a981215a9","tid":1492083,"uid":276215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52d85ae4bd287437600c75d7584c5d8d0bbc9897","tid":1492083,"uid":66221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:20:50.000Z","msg":"趕走小粉紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:24:04.000Z","msg":"光復美國，還我淨土<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38610e2adf25d5008d3fd438db782f5182dc01b2","tid":1492083,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:27:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">【眾籌 Google 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1491396\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1491396</a>"},{"pid":"c18553b778eb3ab2ee07e4eda3d6d408ef7ee0a1","tid":1492083,"uid":276215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e2309b9b12aaa1f1941a18e8bd35fe408e2993e8","tid":1492083,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:20:25.000Z","msg":"Push"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:35:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2596c86b094cf478e828740445f0486f3633b9fd","tid":1492083,"uid":276215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38610e2adf25d5008d3fd438db782f5182dc01b2","tid":1492083,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:27:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">【眾籌 Google 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1491396\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1491